item.title: Seattle Superhero Phoenix Jones Unmasked In Court
item.description: Self-proclaimed superhero Phoenix Jones was forced to reveal his real identity in court due to a case he caught on Sunday. The father and husband, whose real name is Ben Fodor, was arrested for assault because he pepper-sprayed party goers. Jones claims the people were fighting but the folks in question claim they were attacked. item.description: Now that they've been together for ages, people generally associate queen Beyoncé's name with her husband Jay-Z. And though their origin story might not be super-glamorous (Bey reportedly friend-zoned him for years after they initially met), it's clear they're one of music's biggest power couples today. But when Beyoncé's career was first taking off, she had another man on her arm; one who's far lesser-known and seems to be having some major regrets these days about how he treated the former Destiny's Child member.

item.title: Birdman Questions Need For Books While Addressing Inmates
item.description: A clip of Birdman is making rounds on the internet for his commentary on the need for books while speaking to a group of men behind bars. According to Complex, the Hip-Hop entrepreneur visited the Orleans Parish Prison to meet with the inmates and inquire on what he could do to best help their situation. In the video shared on X by the My Mixtapes platform, the New Orleans representative can be heard questioning the need for written text for the imprisoned people.

item.title: TV Shows Still Filming Amid WGA and SAG-AFTRA Strike
item.description: Hollywood came to a standstill amid the joint WGA and SAG-AFTRA strike — but not every TV show has stopped filming. In July 2023, SAG-AFTRA authorized a strike after the Alliance of Motion Picture and Television Producers (AMPTP) did not address any of their concerns regarding fair wages, the use of artificial intelligence and more issues during contract negotiations. The decision came two months after the Writers Guild of America announced their own strike over a labor dispute with the AMPTP — the organization that represents major networks such as Netflix, Amazon, Apple, Disney, Discovery-Warner, NBC Universal, Paramount and Sony.

item.title: What Happened To 'Desperate Housewives' Star Teri Hatcher?
item.description: People say that Teri Hatcher behaved badly on the Desperate Housewives set, but her character, Susan Mayer, was always super sweet. Susan lived on the beautiful Wisteria Lane with her best friends Lynette Scavo, Gabrielle Solis, and Bree Van de Kamp. She raised her daughter Julie after her terrible divorce from Karl and fell in love with the charming Mike Delfino. There is often talk of why Nicolette Sheridan left the show early as her character, Edie Britt, was suddenly gone.

item.title: Elon Musk Becomes The First Person In History To Have A Net Worth Of $300 Billion
item.description: The ongoing game of musical chairs for the top spot of the richest person in the world may have just reached a standstill. Mega billionaire Elon Musk reached a major milestone last month when he became the third person in history to surpass a net worth of $200 billion, subsequently re-earning his spot at the top of the world's wealthiest. Though, the Telsa CEO reached an even more monuments milestone this month when his net worth surpassed $300 billion.

item.title: Brad Pitt Found 'Joy' Out of the 'Misery' of Angelina Jolie Split
item.description: Working on himself. Amid his ongoing drama with Angelina Jolie, Brad Pitt got honest about how making art helped him deal with personal issues. During an interview with Financial Times, which was published on Wednesday, October 12, the actor, 58, opened up about working on sculptures as a Los Angeles art studio following his 2016 split from Jolie, 47. “Our mutual misery became comic,” Pitt said about collaborating with musician Nick Cave and artist Thomas Houseago on an exhibit.

item.title: Casey Rivara GoFundMe: Fundraiser raises over $40,000 for dad who died while helping ducks cross the
item.description: Casey Rivara, a 41-year-old California father of two was lethally hit by a vehicle on May 18 in Rocklin, while he was assisting a gathering of ducks with going across the street. A 17-year-old driver was in the driver’s seat of the vehicle that struck him. Casey’s auntie, Tracey Rivara made a pledge drive page on GoFundMe to help the family during this troublesome time. The pledge drive objective was set at $30,000, yet the family has had the option to raise $75,495 with the assistance of 1,300 gifts as of this composition.

item.title: Travis Kelce Makes Heart Hands in Chiefs' Official Super Bowl Art
item.description: Travis Kelce has copied girlfriend Taylor Swift’s signature heart hands gesture on the NFL field and it’s now been immortalized in official Super Bowl art. The Kansas City Chiefs dropped its official Super Bowl artwork via social media on Tuesday, February 6, in which an illustrated version of Kelce, 34, stood in front of Las Vegas’ famed Bellagio Hotel & Casino resort with teammates Patrick Mahomes, Nick Bolton, L’Jarius Sneed and Trent McDuffie.

item.title: What Will Kate Middleton Be Called When Prince William Is King of England?
item.description: Princess Kate Middleton will be getting a title change when her husband, Prince William, becomes the King of England. Royal historian Marlene Koenig confirmed to Hello! Magazine that Kate will become Queen Catherine. While she will be the sixth Catherine in royal family history, because she’s a queen consort, Kate, 42, will not have a regnal number adjacent with her name. Koenig, who is also the founder of the Royal Musings blog, explained that only the sovereign gets a number after their name.

Extraordinary powers are hunting the shooter who killed something like eight individuals and injured 13 others on Thursday night.

item.title: Angelica Ross Blasts Ryan Murphy Over Missed Marvel Role
item.description: The new Hulu series, The Other Black Girl, triggered something within Angelica Ross, and the Pose and American Horror Story (AHS) actress took to Twitter on Monday (Sept. 18) to call out her former boss, Ryan Murphy. She aired out how his lack of communication caused her to miss out on a role with Marvel that she’d been auditioning for three years. Ross tweeted alleged screenshots from a July 2020 email exchange between her and Murphy regarding a potential AHS series with an all-Black, female-led cast.

item.title: Bella Ramsey Bio, Wiki, Age, Height, Family, Boyfriend, Movies and Net Worth.
item.description: Bella Ramsey Biography Bella Ramsey (born Isabella May Ramsey) is an English actress and singer. She is known for her roles as young noblewoman Lyanna Mormont in the HBO fantasy television series Game of Thrones and Mildred Hubble in the 2017 CBBC television series The Worst Witch. As of 2018, Ramsey currently voices the title character in the Netflix animated series Hilda. Bella Ramsey Age Ramsey is 18 years old as of 2020, he was born on 25 September 2003, in Nottingham, England.She celebrates her birthday on 25 September every year and her birth sign is Libra.

item.title: Brooklyn Nets' Star Kevin Durant Launches A $200 Million SPAC Firm
item.description: It was recently announced that the Brooklyn Nets forward, Kevin Durant, is furthering his ventures off the SPAC business. Similar to fellow sports stars Serena Williams and Shaquille O'Neal, Durant is backing a blank check firm. The NBA star joins forces with Infinite Acquisition Corp, fresh off the tails of it filing for up to $200 million in initial public offerings. Durant's leading investment firm, Thirty Five Venture, was listed on the filing as a sponsor within a fifty-fifty partnership with the manager and partner Rich Kleiman.

item.title: How Old Is Gary Kaltbaum And Wife? Pictures and Photos On Wikipedia Bio
item.description: Who is Gary Kaltbaum wife? He is a licensed investment advisor with over 30 years of market expertise.  He is the founder and president of Kaltbaum Capital Management, an Orlando-based financial investment advising firm. He is a Fox News Channel Business Contributor who regularly appears on the Fox Business Network and Fox News Channel. Gary now serves on the Boys & Girls Clubs of Central Florida board, where he previously served as Chairman of the Board.

item.title: Kroy Biermann Publicly Pleads For Kim Zolciak To Agree To Sell Atlanta Mansion Amid $1 Million Debt
item.description: Kim Zolciak was able to avoid losing her home to foreclosure earlier this year, but it doesn’t look like the reality star will be staying in it much longer, thanks to her ongoing divorce from Kroy Biermann, who re-filed for divorce this month after calling off his initial request in July. Kroy’s attorney Marlys A. Bergstrom revealed to Us Weekly that the former NFL star is putting pressure on his estranged wife to sell their Atlanta mansion ASAP given their financial situation.

item.title: Laura Dern Admits Stressful Single Parenting Is Overwhelming
item.description: Doing it on her own! Laura Dern welcomed a son and daughter with her ex-husband, Ben Harper, before their 2013 split — and she’s opening up about single parenting. “On good days, I am kind enough to remember that there are growing pains, and it is all overwhelming and not easy or always fun,” the actress, 52, admitted toModern Luxury in her September 2019 cover story. “On the hard days, it’s stressful and there is too much going on as a single parent—and it can be hard to carve out a minute for yourself.

item.title: Skip the Salon With This Viral Lash Lift Kit 49% Off If Youre Fast
item.description: Us Weekly has affiliate partnerships. We receive compensation when you click on a link and make a purchase. Learn more! Lash lifts are all the rage these days. We can finally put down the curler — and maybe even the mascara — and enjoy “naturally” lifted lashes for weeks (or even months) at a time. The only issue? The cost. The inconvenience of booking an appointment isn’t our favorite either.

item.title: Stephen A. Smith Says JAY-Z Checked Him Over Beyonc, Rihanna Remarks
item.description: Stephen A. Smith claims JAY-Z called him after he took to a talk show comparing wife Beyoncé to his Roc Nation artist, Rihanna. Ahead of Riri’s 2023 Super Bowl Halftime Show, Smith shared his opinion that the Caribbean artist wouldn’t hold a candle to Beyoncé’s previous showings. “A month later, Hov and I were on the phone,” Smith revealed on the Connect the Dots podcast Monday (March 4). “Hov was like, ‘My dawg, you family, that’s family.

item.title: The Richest Australian Cricket Players, And How They Amassed Huge Fortunes
item.description: Quick LinksJosh Hazlewood Marcus Stoinis Adam Zampa Nathan Coulter-Nile Aaron Finch David Warner Glenn Maxwell Mitchell Starc Steve Smith Pat Cummins Highlights Famed cricketer David Warner plans to retire after his 100th T20 International match against West Indies in June 2024. Australia's wealthiest cricketers include Aaron Finch with a net worth of $11 million and Mitchell Starc with a net worth of $21 million.

item.title: Who Are the Montana Boyz? Kristin Cavallaris BF Is in TikTok Group
item.description: The Montana Boyz are the latest TikTok stars taking over the social media platform — and one is even dating Kristin Cavallari. Mark Estes, Kaleb Campbell Winterburn and Kade Wilcox began making videos in 2021 and have since risen to fame, amassing over 460,000 followers on the app and counting. The three-member group shares videos dancing to music and showing off their cowboy lifestyle. They’ve also dabbled with modeling, posing for their Montana-based brand Belmont Acres Clothing and sharing a behind-the-scenes look at the shoot via TikTok in October 2023.

If you want to take the best care of your skin that you possibly can, you absolutely need sunscreen. You should also invest in a good eye cream. Those are two things you’ll appreciate having one day when you’re older. So no matter what age you are now, it’s a good idea to go ahead and get one of each and start using them.

item.title: This Is How Rebel Wilson Started And Grew Her $22 Million Empire
item.description: Quick LinksGetting Started in The Entertainment Scene Struggling to Make Ends Meet Breaking Through Her Financial Struggles Australian actress and comedian Rebel Wilson has impressively accumulated a cool $22 million net worth but just a few years ago her bank account barely had a penny in it. The Australian star revealed that she had troubles with her finances a few years back. Although she has been working her ass off since she moved to Los Angeles in 2010, it was only in 2015 when she was able to earn a decent amount of money.

item.title: 15 Pop Culture Icons From The 90s Who Have Managed To Stay Relevant Today
item.description: Staying relevant sometimes can be considered a talent in itself as it's not as easy as it may seem. The '90s was a wild decade and contained so many iconic pop culture figures. From teen sensations, iconic actors, to killer music videos, it's a decade that is close to a lot of people's hearts. Whether you were one of those people who had butterfly clips in your hair, wore platform shoes or had posters of Eminem on your wall, it's safe to say the '90s was a decade for expressing yourself.

item.title: Candace Cameron Bure Defends Leaving Hallmark for GAC
item.description: Candace Cameron Bure is not looking back after her Hallmark departure. When asked in an Instagram Story Q&A on Wednesday, May 29, why Cameron Bure, 48, decided to exit the network, she replied, “It wasn’t so much about leaving as it was about an opportunity to grow a new network that puts faith and family at the forefront of its content. I’m very proud of the work I did at Hallmark for 15 years and love all my friends there.

item.title: Colleen Ballinger Gives Birth, Welcomes Twins With Erik Stocklin
item.description: Surprise! Colleen Ballinger and Erik Stocklin welcomed their twins early at 32 weeks along. “My sweet babies decided to come early,” the YouTuber, 34, captioned her Wednesday, November 10, Instagram reveal. “Go see the magical chaos that happened this weekend.” The California native shared her birth story via YouTube, beginning by telling son Flynn, 2, that her water had broken in bed. After straightening her hair and driving to the hospital with Stocklin, 39, Ballinger found out that she had an umbilical cord complication and needed an emergency C-section.

item.title: How Comedian Chelsea Handler Spends Her $35 Million Net Worth
item.description: Throughout Chelsea Handler’s lengthy career, she has managed to accomplish an awful lot. Best known as a mainstay of television for many years, Handler was the host of her own TV show for nearly a decade. With that in mind, it makes all the sense in the world that Handler has amassed a $35 million fortune as of the time of this writing, according to celebritynetworth.com. Of course, Chelsea Handler is far from the only celebrity who has access to a great fortune.

item.title: Jujimufu Biography, Wife, Height, Age, Other Facts You Need To Know
item.description: The journey of a thousand miles, they say, begins with a safe and dedicated stage. A little boy from Alabama started his fitness journey in 1999 with the goal of improving his height and strength. True to his passion, he not only succeeded but also garnered a host of followers after him over the years. This personality was born Jon Call but became known to us as Jujimufu, the anabolic acrobat. He is something of an anomaly in the world of strength and bodybuilding.

item.title: Prince William Net Worth How Much is Prince William Worth?
item.description: Prince William, the Duke of Cambridge, is a prominent member of the British royal family. He has gained substantial wealth through a combination of inheritance, military service, and his position as the Duke of Cornwall. Let’s take a closer look at Prince William’s financial status and explore how he has amassed his fortune. Key Takeaways: Prince William’s net worth is estimated to be around $100 million. He inherited a significant fortune, including a trust fund from his great-grandmother, the Queen Mother.

item.title: Stacey Pullen Dazzles With Dance.Here.Now Debut At Cielo NYC
item.description: Stacey Pullen is a man about town as of late. Within the last four months, the Detroit techno/tech house DJ and innovator has graced the decks of 4 different venues around the city with his well crafted late night sets. Last Thursday, he made his debut at Cielo at the popular Dance.Here.Now. party. With a capacity limit of just 325, Cielo was the perfect venue to get up close and personal with the man himself.

item.title: Stavros Halkias Net Worth How Much Is Stavros Halkias Worth?
item.description: Stavros Halkias, a renowned comedian and podcast host, has built a successful career that has led to substantial financial success. As of 2023, his estimated net worth is around $800,000. Halkias’ wealth stems from his involvement in stand-up comedy and podcasting. While his annual salary is approximately $20,000, he also earns sizeable speaking fees ranging from $50,000 to $100,000. His diverse professional endeavors have allowed him to establish a solid financial foundation.

item.description: Quick LinksNaked Singularity (2021) The Model (2016) Kill Your Friends (2015) Northmen: A Viking Saga (2014) If Beale Street Could Talk (2018) The Transporter Refueled (2015) Midway (2019) Alita: Battle Angel (2019) Maleficent: Mistress Of Evil (2019) Deadpool (2016) Hailing from London, England, Ed Skrein began his acting career in 2012 when he starred in three back-to-back movies, Piggy, The Sweeney, and Ill Manors as a supporting actor.

item.description: Welcome to the Toyota 4RUNNER Forum, the ultimate online community for all Toyota 4RUNNER enthusiasts. Whether you’re a proud owner or simply a fan of this iconic SUV, our forum is the perfect place to connect with fellow 4RUNNER enthusiasts, share experiences, and gain valuable insights. item.title: Who Has Played The Most Roles Since The Show Ended?
item.description: The Office is one of the most beloved series in the history of television. With its cast of uncanny, whimsical characters and its tale of a struggling paper company trying desperately to stay afloat all while being filmed for a documentary, it was certainly a long-running hit. Though the wacky antics of one Michael G. Scott were not met with immediate success, the show eventually ended up coming into its own and became a runaway smash.

item.title: 'OITNB" Actor Brad William Henke Dead at Age 56: 5 Things to Know
item.description: A shocking loss. Orange Is the New Black alum Brad William Henke has died. He was 56. “Brad was an incredibly kind man of joyous energy,” Henke’s manager, Matt DelPiano, said in a statement to TMZ on Thursday, December 1. “A very talented actor, he loved being a part of this community….and we loved him back. Our thoughts are with his wife and family.” According to Deadline, Henke died in his sleep on Tuesday, November 29.

item.title: Why are therapists called shrinks
item.description: Why are shrinks called shrinks? Shrink derives from “headshrinker,” a word that was initially popularized by reports of the distinctive headhunting practice of the Amazonian Jivaro people. The word “shrink” has long been a common way of referring to psychotherapists, including both psychiatrists and psychologists. What does shrink mean therapist? n. slang for a psychologist, psychiatrist, or other mental health professional who conducts psychotherapy. It is short for headshrinker, an allusion to the practice of headshrinking.

item.title: Former One Direction Members: Where Are They Now?
item.description: One Direction may be on an extended hiatus, but Harry Styles, Niall Horan, Liam Payne, Louis Tomlinson and Zayn Malik have continued to make music — and headlines — over the years. After forming and finishing in third place on the U.K.’s version of The X Factor in 2010, One Direction released four successful studio albums — Up All Night, Take Me Home, Midnight Memories and Four. item.title: The Jersey Shore Series Goes On A Family Vacation
item.description: The television reality series Jersey Shore ran on the MTV channel from 2009 to 2012. The show followed the antics of eight housemates who lived together for sun and fun during the summers on the shores of the State of New Jersey. The popularity of the American show was copied with foreign versions in England as Geordie Shore, in Spain as Gandia Shore, and in Mexico as Acapulco Shore. After the series was canceled, a reunion special of the show called Jersey Shore: Reunion Road Trip was aired during August 2017.

item.title: Wyclef Jean Calls For Tsu Surf's Freedom During 2023 MTV VMAs
item.description: Wyclef Jean gave a huge shoutout to incarcerated rapper Tsu Surf during the 2023 MTV VMAs, calling for the battle rap star’s freedom. On Tuesday (Sept. 12), Jean was at the VMAs to present Shakira with the 2023 MTV Video Vanguard Award on Tuesday night, where he shouted his fellow Brick City rep. “Right about now, New Jerusalem, New Jersey!
